race.comment: MONEY TEAM (5) bounced off his eye-catching third at Eagle Farm, with a dominant win in fast time over 1300m at Warwick Farm in BM78 class. Stalks the good speed and looks the testing material again. CARBONADOS (6) underrated gelding who comes up from Victoria with a smart fresh record. Fitted with the two good jump outs and looks ready to go with Rawiller booked from the low draw. MIDNIGHT OPAL (4) knocked up late on resumption when fifth over 1200m at this track. Since fitted with a searching 1000m trial placing at Newcastle. Back in grade and gets every chance with Nock's 2kg claim. HEURISTIC (9) win record hardly excites but did close off okay at his first run back when sixth over this trip at Warwick Farm. Look for him late.
